 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/uraloth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Raloth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Administrator</span><br>  Posts: 838<br> <font color=#8B4513>(7/25/01 4:58:23 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.canadiancommentary.com/head.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Farwell</span><hr size=1> I have heard about this guild chat incident, and the vulgar things said.  Telak has left the guild, as he is aware that his humor is not a good fit for VF.<br>
<br>
I urge anyone who has left VF over this to reconsider why they are leaving, and who caused them to leave.<br>
<br>
This type of language you mention will not be tolerated in Victus Fortis and the whole mess shall be cleaned up in no time.  It just takes awhile to manage things like this.  We are not a guild that just throws down the hammer of justice on a moments notice.  Instead we have proper channels by which to lodge complaints in privacy.  This was down two nights ago, and there has been a discussion of the event.  Since then it has erupted again, and Telak has left the guild because he realized his vulgar humor is not wanted here.<br>
<br>
Such sexually explicit language won't be tolerated here in this Guild, you have my word and the agreeement of the High Council on that.   <br>
<br>
Take care,<br>
<br>
Raloth  <p><img src=http://www.canadiancommentary.com/everquest/images/ralothsig2.JPG></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/uraloth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Raloth</A> at: 7/25/01 5:00:21 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/uveleskia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Veleskia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 8<br> <font color=#8B4513>(7/25/01 6:12:25 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Farewell</span><hr size=1> Raloth,<br>
<br>
I'm sorry you had to come back to Norrath to settle all of this mess, and I truly hope that happens. I holding nothing against Telak or Inouva, I just feel that their conversation was very, very offending. My 10 year old brother does not need to hear this, nor do I want to see if myself.<br>
<br>
I was told repeatedly to turn off my guild chat, NO. I have every right to listen to what my guild has to say, might be pretty important. <br>
<br>
My best wishes for each and everyone of you.<br>
<br>
Please be safe and may you ding many times!<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/beverquestersofnorrath.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=galadriaculravenni>Galadria Culravenni</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 496<br> <font color=#8B4513>(7/25/01 7:59:00 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Farwell</span><hr size=1> I am so sorry this happened. My apologies to the both of you and anyone else who has left because of it, and I hope we see you soon rejoining us. I know what happened is NOT my fault, but...<br>
<br>
~Galadria <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/uraloth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Raloth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Administrator</span><br>  Posts: 843<br> <font color=#8B4513>(7/25/01 8:17:54 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.canadiancommentary.com/head.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Farwell</span><hr size=1> Aye, if anyone left over this please consider coming back.  This guild will not put up with this kind of attitude, and now that it has been rectified, the matter will become strict policy, so anyone who does this in the future will be removed from our group.<br>
<br>
It did take a few days to get the cogs moving, and that is in part to me getting settled in at home after my trip, and my brother is in town visiting.  I wish I could have been online at the time it happened, but I wasn't.<br>
<br>
The Council is wholly against this behaviour and it won't happen again.  Please consider coming back to us, as we miss you very very much, and it hurts me personally that some new member could cause so much damage in so little time.  Telak is gone, and we will be contacting Inouva for a lengthy apology and any further action the Council decides upon.<br>
<br>
Once again I am very sorry.  I have  young children as well (3 of them) and I would not want them to see distastefull jokes like that as well.  <br>
<br>
Take care,<br>
<br>
Raloth <p><img src=http://www.canadiancommentary.com/everquest/images/ralothsig2.JPG></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub44.ezboard.com/utaallon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Taallon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 299<br> <font color=#8B4513>(7/25/01 6:34:28 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.fbe.unsw.edu.au/staff/graham.hannah/eq/resources/taallon60x60.jpg  WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Farwell</span><hr size=1> Just to add my 2 cents,<br>
